---
title: Mild Indian Lamb Loin & Roasted Cauliflower with Coconut Sauce, Mint Yoghurt & Flatbreads
description: A sumptuous lamb feast with a sub-continental twist. This tender lamb rump is spiced with a mild warming curry paste, then
paired with crispy roasted vegetables and a creamy mint yoghurt. Don’t forget to rest your lamb for 10 minutes after cooking for
the perfect slices that are blushing and moist.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-indian-lamb-loin-roast-cauliflower-1efdaad3.jpg
